## NANO BANANA PROMPT STRUCTURE

Each prompt must follow this structure:

```
Using the exact uploaded image as base, change ONLY the nail design on the fingers. Keep everything else completely identical — hand position, skin tone, rings, jewelry, background, lighting, shadows, and composition.

New nail design: [Specific description of new design — color, pattern, finish, nail art details, style]

The new design should reflect [board topic] aesthetic. Nail shape remains [shape from image]. Result should look like a real salon photograph.
```

