## SEO NAMING CULTURE (Non-Negotiable)

**Title always starts with what is written ON the pin:**
- Pin has overlay text → title starts with those exact words
- No overlay text → title starts with specific design name (never board name)
- Collection pin → starts with number

**Description always mirrors title start:**
- First 4-5 words of description = first 4-5 words of title, word for word

**Board name placement:**
- Never at the start of title or description
- Can appear naturally in description body only

